            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <img src="/icons/plus-user-profile-svgrepo-com.svg" class="h-10 w-10 mb-4" alt="" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#86B84C]">Teamwork</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
              Leadership and collaboration with diverse teams.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <img src="/icons/alt-square-quill-svgrepo-com.svg" class="h-10 w-10 mb-4" alt="" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#86B84C]">Continuous learning</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
              Always learning new tools and better practices.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <img src="/icons/left-text-bubble-svgrepo-com.svg" class="h-10 w-10 mb-4" alt="" />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#86B84C]">Purposeful leadership</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
